2004-08-20  Synge Todo  <wistaria@comp-phys.org>
	
	* [alps/bindings] Removed alps/bindings/gels.hpp

	* [boost/bindings] Added a script for importing bindings headers
	  (config/import-bindings.hpp).
	  Updated to the latest CVS snapshot (tag = BINDINGS_20040820).

	* [ietl] Added a script for importing IETL headers
	  (config/import-ietl.hpp).
	  Imported IETL version 2.1 (tag = IETL_2_1).
	
2004-08-18  Matthias Troyer <troyer@comp-phys.org>

	* [model,example] Added fermion sign support

